title: Will's Deli
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Salad bar, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This small delicatessen offers vegetarian and sometimes vegan cooked lunches on a daily basis, complete with an extensive salad bar. Sells a small range of groceries, including cereals, dairy-free milks, and egg-free mayo. A stone's throw away from Somerville and St Anne's, the Radcliffe Humanities building and the Mathematical Institute on Woodstock Road.
